Package: ucLoader
Title: Unity Catalog File IO Helpers for R on Databricks
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Mackenzie", "Ridout", , "Mackenzie.Ridout@defra.gov.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Convenience helpers to access files stored in Databricks Unity
    Catalog Volumes from R. Supports downloading via the Databricks REST API
    and loading into an R session (e.g., reading CSV or loading .RData), and
    saving objects back to Unity Catalog. Intended for RStudio Server on
    Databricks where the workspace URL and personal access token are provided
    via environment variables (DATABRICKS_HOST, DATABRICKS_TOKEN). Does not
    require the /Volumes FUSE mount.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
